      <h1>Shadow OS v1.1 Release: Enhanced Privacy Features</h1>
      <p class="post-date">April 1, 2025</p>
      <div class="post-content">
        <p>We’re excited to announce the release of <strong>Shadow OS v1.1</strong>! This update brings a host of new features and improvements based on community feedback and our ongoing commitment to privacy and performance.</p>
        <p>Here’s what’s new in v1.1:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Enhanced Encryption Tools</strong>: New options for encrypting files and communications with ease.</li>
          <li><strong>Improved Firewall</strong>: Better protection against unauthorized network access.</li>
          <li><strong>Performance Boost</strong>: Reduced resource usage for a smoother experience.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>To upgrade to v1.1, head over to our download page or follow the instructions in the documentation. We’d love to hear your feedback as we continue to refine Shadow OS!</p>
        <p><a href="/download.html">Download v1.1</a> | <a href="/docs/update-v1-1.html">Update Guide</a></p>
